      "text": "Thine An-gel who pro-claimed, O Lord, the ho-ly Res-ur-rec--tion, caused the guard-i-ans to be a-fraid and ad-dressed the wom-en’s fear thus by say-ing: Where-fore seek__ ye the Liv-ing a-mong the dead? He is ris-en as God, and e-ter-nal life__ hath He grant--ed un-to__ the__ world."
